data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful updated home in sought after Glenhurst subdivision in Wentzville! This home hosts an open floor concept offering a kitchen/living room combo with ample natural light! The 2nd floor holds 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The master bedroom has a large walk in closet. The basement is unfinished, but is clean and dry ready for you to make your own! 
This home is centrally located to shopping, restaurants, schools, & parks! Very close to highway 70 or 64/40!
